      "id": 16,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Triage Runbook\n\n1. If `transfer_fail_keys` rises while `no_available_handle_keys` stays flat, jump to transport logs first.\n2. Grep handshake-layer signals:\n\n```bash\nrg -n \"\\\\[Handshake\\\\] Failed to modify QP to RTR|Invalid argument: received packet mismatch|Cannot make connection for endpoint\" bench_results/<run_dir> -g '*.log'\n```\n\n3. Grep transfer and batch symptoms:\n\n```bash\nrg -n \"Failed to complete transfers after 60 seconds|Transfer failed for key|Operation for key|batch_put failed\" bench_results/<run_dir> -g '*.log'\n```\n\n4. Current hotspot from the April 15 analysis: `prefill-1-gb200-rack1-04.log` and `prefill-0-gb200-rack1-03.log` in `bench_results/pd_kimi_nsys_prefill6_light/prefill_6_mtc_18/`.\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Triage Runbook",
